Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了就回答我吧  星  在哪…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱纱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃铃  注意脚下  有个悬崖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱纱  振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像扭到脚了
